Summary: This section details the properties of the SkeletonModification2DCCDIK class.

Properties
* ccdik_data_chain_length (int): The length of the CCDIK data chain. Default: 0.
* target_nodepath (NodePath): The NodePath to the target node for the CCDIK solver. Default: NodePath("").
* tip_nodepath (NodePath): The NodePath to the tip node for the CCDIK solver. Default: NodePath("").
